COMPONENT OVERVIEW
==================

This directory contains the Vibrante-Node Houdini Integration Plugin
("the Plugin"), which provides:

  • A JSON-RPC command server (vibrante_hou_server.py) that runs inside
    a live SideFX Houdini session and exposes a TCP bridge for node
    creation, parameter manipulation, cooking, and code execution.

  • Launch and environment management (vibrante_node_houdini.py) that
    starts the Vibrante-Node subprocess from Houdini with the correct
    environment variables and port bindings.

  • A curated Houdini node library (v_nodes_houdini/) and script
    collection (v_scripts_houdini/) that integrate natively with the
    Vibrante-Node visual pipeline graph.

  • Houdini package configuration (vibrante_node.json) for zero-config
    installation via Houdini's package discovery system.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

LICENSE CLASSIFICATION
======================

The Houdini Integration Plugin is classified as an Enterprise DCC
Integration under the Vibrante-Node open-core licensing model.

  COMPONENT                        LICENSE
