RESTRICTIONS
=============

Regardless of license tier, the following are prohibited:

  1. Distributing or sublicensing the Plugin to third parties without
     a separate OEM agreement.
  2. Removing or obscuring copyright notices, license headers, or
     attribution strings from any Plugin file.
  3. Using the Plugin to develop a competing Houdini-to-node-graph
     integration product without a separate written agreement.
  4. Circumventing the AGPLv3 network-use disclosure obligation for
     any modified open-source component of Vibrante-Node that the
     Plugin interacts with.

